  {
    icon: '📐',
    title: 'Qualifies Gas Project Scope Online',
    text: "Through conversation, the AI determines whether the visitor needs a boiler replacement, a landlord CP12, an annual service, a full heating system, or a gas emergency. You receive a classified lead with the correct scope."
  },
  {
    icon: '🕐',
    title: 'Converts Evening Boiler Failures',
    text: "Boilers fail after the office closes — the heating cuts out at 8pm, the fault code appears at 10pm, the hot water stops at 11pm. Homeowners search your website for a Gas Safe engineer while the house cools around them. Chat captures their fault code and urgency."
