    text: `Website chat is bundled with phone answering at £${pricing.tiers.core.price}/month. Unlimited gas conversations — from annual service bookings to twenty-plot boiler installation tenders.`
  }
];

const faqs = [
  {
    question: "How do I install chat on my gas engineering website?",
    answer: "Onboarding delivers a single JavaScript snippet to paste into your website header through WordPress, Wix, Squarespace, or your HTML editor. The branded chat widget appears on every page immediately. Gas firms with boiler installation galleries and Gas Safe accreditation prominently displayed find that visitors engage with chat directly from pages showing neat Worcester Bosch installations with Benchmark certificates."
  },
  {
    question: "Can the AI advise on boiler selections?",
    answer: "Your Gas Safe company profile trains the AI with your preferred manufacturers, output sizing approach, and system recommendations. When a visitor types 'what combi is best for a 3-bed semi with 2 bathrooms?' the AI responds from your configured preferences — mentioning suitable output ranges, flow rates, and brands — while gathering the property type, the radiator count, and the current boiler details."
  },
  {
    question: "What does chat capture from gas visitors?",
    answer: "The AI collects the gas requirement (boiler replacement, service, CP12, new installation, or emergency), the existing boiler manufacturer and approximate age, the system type, the property size and bathroom count, the fault code if applicable, the urgency, and the visitor's contact information for your callback."
  },
  {
    question: "Does chat slow my gas engineering website?",
    answer: "Boiler installation photography, Gas Safe registration badges, manufacturer warranty logos, and Trustpilot review widgets load at their full speed before chat activates. The lightweight widget loads asynchronously after all existing page content renders. Zero impact on page performance or search ranking."
  },
  {
    question: "Is website chat a separate charge?",
    answer: `Chat comes included with phone answering at £${pricing.tiers.core.price}/month — zero extra. Gas engineers benefit from overlapping coverage: daytime phone calls from developers booking new-build gas packages and landlords scheduling CP12 programmes, paired with evening and weekend website chats from homeowners whose boilers have just failed and are searching desperately for a Gas Safe engineer before bedtime.`
  },
  {
    question: "How is visitor data from gas queries handled?",
    answer: "Chat conversations containing property addresses, boiler model numbers and serial numbers, fault codes, Gas Safe notification references, and visitor contact details are encrypted and stored on UK and EU servers under UK GDPR. Leads go exclusively to you. No gas project details reach competitors or third-party lead generators."
